{"type": "article", "id": 21930, "title": "这条护城河的周边变成了游客中心，是朴实的好设计", "description": "护城河道下面有 3 层停车场和 1040 个停车位。", "date": "2016-02-05T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4026, "name": "荷兰"}, {"id": 14123, "name": "景观设计"}, {"id": 23165, "name": "Studio Leon Thier"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 82, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702161221svYjCEbeZNyhM3nQ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>在荷兰 ’s-Hertogenbosch （斯海尔托亨博思）市，建筑事务所 <a href=\"http://www.studioleonthier.nl/\">Studio Leon Thier</a> 被政府委托改建护城河步道。除了要保护护城河和历史遗迹外，还要尽可能增加多的停车位，将这里变成游客中心。</p>\n<p>这个项目从 2011 年就开始启动了，直到 2015 年 7 月才真正开放。这不是一件容易的事，所谓护城河早已因为填海造陆而有些面目全非，而要在很窄的空间里设计行人和车流的路线也需要精细的安排。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161205QS2AYpKvkwUHFRhj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">从前</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161205ObWlotmfzerkqPU2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">规划</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>在现在的设计里，河道被重新梳理了，沿着河边建立了红色的河提以供行人通行。在一片绿色的自然中，红色显得格外清晰明亮。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161206iA8Ne9pXaTLwrzxE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>一条木桥横跨两岸，它是倾斜的，贴近河面，窄而长。桥梁本身的设计并不复杂，却格外地融入在自然环境中。</p>\n<p class=\"\">穿过木桥达到石洞一样的门口，直接通向一个中世纪景点 Casino garden。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161207GDegaSv5hkWTbnEl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161208QX9Sl31y28sJCTrv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161208E3bGS0YsvwXteq8B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">河流的转折处有一个圆形的枢纽，行人经过之后是延伸的红色步道，与圆形的枢纽呈左右对称。只是不再是沿河而建，两边是道路和绿化带。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161209Q6nw8Bmd95VNWIua.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161209s6jxft5zD2vG94Lm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161210hZsPQXt5rKgIH0Fo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">中间的圆形枢纽是一个重要的螺旋车道，连接了地下三层的大型停车场，一共有 1040 个停车位，它们都建在了护城河的下面。</p>\n<p class=\"\">设计师的出发点是停车场要建在舒适的环境里，让开车过来的游客可以很容易找到车位。停车场在开发后，获得了ESPA（European Standard Parking Award 欧洲标准停车场）颁发的金奖。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161210nYfFK2u8T7iypbhz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161211MXrGAjc17Y43Oi0b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161212aXQKqDV206EdtR5x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161212BQyc3V08lp7uNR2k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161214mtPhwgE5sFBQ0Xnq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161215c406jMTSr87pQVRy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021612176kShpdVGzCtAUYDT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6787037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161217X9V3wrlmRun0daqA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161218dVUq2x8wZjvQBrAy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161219OzXdl3sxPh79gKCb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161220B4SGoFCg57eNPUZc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161220Bm61p82wyD5AZfiI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自<a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/781344/zuiderpark-stadswalzone-studio-leon-thier\">archdaily</a>、<a href=\"http://www.studioleonthier.nl/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Studio Leon Thier</a></p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p> </p>\n\n"}